ks. They have no physical form, but they can project their presence on holo=
graphic displays or video screens.</span></p><p style=3D"margin-top:0pt; ma=
rgin-bottom:10pt; font-size:10pt"><span style=3D"font-family:Verdana; color=
:#a5a5a5">They are assisted by small robots called Helpernoids, who build a=
nd maintain all of the machinery for the Mechanoid civilization.</span></p>=
<p style=3D"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:10pt"><span style=
=3D"font-family:Verdana; color:#a5a5a5">No one seems to know where the Mech=
